{"tid":494662,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Justice League》作台階 - Aquaman 獨立電影首張劇照曝光","createTime":"2017-12-10T00:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T03:32:59.000Z","uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a507dd805ae0635f767692e509ed61ae8b3c62b4","tid":494662,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/082712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F082712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e227c406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDC Comics 的英雄大片《Justice League》已上畫了一段時間，相信各位有看電影的朋友也知道是次為「水行俠」Aquaman 首度正式亮相，而 DC Comics 亦將會在下年為 Aquaman 推出獨立電影，並依然由 Jason Momoa 飾演。找來曾拍攝《Saw》、《The Conjuring》等精彩恐怖電影的導演溫子仁執導，相信定必為英雄電影再創新高峰，同時為戲迷帶來驚喜！溫子仁在接受《Entertainment Weekly》的查詢時表示：<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s going to look very different, it will feel very different &mdash; aesthetically, tonally, story-wise &mdash; it&rsquo;s my own take. It&rsquo;s a much more a traditional action-adventure quest movie.<br />\n<br />\n同時，DC Comics 亦為《Entertainment Weekly》帶來電影的首張劇照，從照片可以看出與《Justice League》內的 Aquaman 有所不同，眼神當中亦充滿殺氣，這相信就是溫子仁想要帶出的感覺。而故事亦將講述男主角 Arthur Curry 如何成為 Aquaman 的經過及坎坷的身世。而由 Amber Heard 飾演的 Aquaman 女友「Mera」已在早前於溫子仁的 Instagram 中曝光，電影暫定於 2018 年 12 月 21 日上映。而在 DC Comics 以 Aquaman 出擊前夕，Marvel 將會先以 7 部電影作強攻，想知道的朋友可打開這裡了解。到底 Aquaman 能否以 1 敵 7 並大獲好評呢？"},{"pid":"6255653d3359cbcbde9aea7d1b601418c251ab96","tid":494662,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"DC好似靠導演功力多d"},{"pid":"a1890d388be0c5b687ef2adaa35cb68c666f1f80","tid":494662,"uid":17619,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:54:50.000Z","msg":"依然好黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個畫面"},{"pid":"b1b994ffbd4aa05f4d6b228db52ff3bca943f09c","tid":4946